            <title>Casio 推出全新手錶戒指，外觀儼如小型 G-Shock 可顯示時間兼計時</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/17/casios-first-watch-ring/parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=casios-first-watch-ring</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/17/casios-first-watch-ring/parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 05:00:27 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CASIO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[G-Shock]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手錶]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智能戒指]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275522</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近來陸續有廠商推出智能戒指，而 Casio 最近推出的戒指雖然不是那麼「智能」，但仍然相當實用。<br /><span id="more-1275522"></span></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_73648"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_43hR7QccSM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_01jp-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_01jp-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_01jp.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這款型號為 CRW-001-1JR 的手錶戒指是為了慶祝 Casio 推出數碼手錶 50 週年而製作，外觀仿似 Casio 在 1983 年推出的經典全金屬 G-Shock 5000 手錶，在不足一吋的錶殼下，仍然可以顯示時、分、秒。戒指還配備三個功能按鈕，可控制額外功能，如顯示日期、不同時區時間和碼錶功能。此外竟然更具備背光功能，可以選擇閃爍顯示取代聲音的鬧鐘功能。手錶由單一電池供電，Casio 表示可使用約兩年，而且易於更換。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_02jp-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_02jp-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw0011_feature_02jp.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Casio 表示，為了精確重現這款戒指手錶所基於的大型數碼手錶的設計和精緻細節，採用了金屬粉末注射成型工藝，將其製作成單一零件。而 CRW-001-1JR 的尺寸只有日規 22 號（香港的 24 號）。如果是手指較小的用家，可以使用附帶的墊片（日規 19/16 號，香港 22/18 號）來改善配戴效果。CRW-001-1JR 將於 12 月在日本上市，售價 19,800 日圓（約 128 美元）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw001_packagepngcop-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw001_packagepngcop-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/crw001_packagepngcop.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.casio.com/jp/watches/casio/product.CRW-001-1/">Casio</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
